value_stack::push_int64

Push a number onto the stack.

Synopsis 
void
push_int64(
    int64_t i);
Description

This function pushes a number value onto the stack.

Exception Safety

Basic guarantee. Calls to memory_resource::allocate may throw.

Parameters

Name

Description

i

The number to insert.
